At the beginning of this lecture,
I asked the question

218
00:11:30,152 --> 00:11:33,402
as to what the 2nd most consumed 
substance after water?

219
00:11:34,315 --> 00:11:36,702
And I'm sure
 you have the answer by now,

220
00:11:36,902 --> 00:11:41,265
but in case you don't,
then the correct answer is:

221
